
README-notes
2019-2-3


Origin
========

remote.origin.url=git://opencircuitdesign.com/qflow-1.3


Build
=======

Dependent packages built in this order:

    magic, netgen, qrouter, graywolf, yosys

Build commands:

    ./configure --with-graywolf=<graywolf-prefix-path>/bin \
                --with-netgen=<netgen-prefix-path>/bin     \
                --with-qrouter=<qrouter-prefix-path>/bin   \
                --with-yosys=<yosys-prefix-path>/usr/local/bin  \
                --with-magic=<magic-prefix-path>/bin       \
                --prefix=<prefix-path>
    make
    make install


Runtime depency
=================

 install python3-tkinter


Tutorial
==========

 technology lib (this step is not required for qflow 1.3)
  http://opencircuitdesign.com/qflow/welcome.html

    wget http://vlsiarch.ecen.okstate.edu/flows/MOSIS_SCMOS/osu_soc_v2.7/osu_soc_v2.7.tar.gz
    mkdir osu_soc_v2.7
    cd osu_soc_v2.7
    tar xf ../osu_soc_v2.7.tar.gz

 run commands: 

    mkdir test
    cd test
    wget http://opencircuitdesign.com/qflow/example/map9v3.v
    #qflow gui
    qflow -T osu035 map9v3

   remove comments in qflow_exec.sh and run it.

 run gui: 

    mkdir test
    cd test
    mkdir source layout synthesis
    cp .../map9v3.v source
    qflow -T osu035 gui

   it runs ok with prep, synth, place, static timing, rout, post rout sta, migrate, drc, 
   but fails at lvs, not to gds.


Performance
=============

 host windows 10 2018 feature 09, intel i7 6700HQ 2.6GHz 2601Mhz
 virtual machine 4x60% cpu, 8192M memory

    time cost in seconds for steps
                synth    place    route   
      map9v3    4.22     38.51    3.15    
      picorv32  1m54.98  127m     31m6.11(failed)


